high_descs: Take a step to the right and approach the coffeetable in front of you.
Pick up the butterknife from the table.
Turn right and head straight to the apple in the kitchen corner.
Cut an apple inside the sink with the cutter.
Take a small step aside, to the left of the sink.
Put the butterknife on the sink.
Take a step back to the sink.
Pick up an apple slice from the sink.
Turn around and move to a microwave on your right where you can see a microwave.
Put the apple slice in the microwave, let it heat up for a while, and take it out.
Go to the coffeetable in the opposite side of the hall.
Lean over the coffeetable and put the apple slice behind it.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated-up apple behind the low CoffeeTable

high_descs: Turn right and take few steps and again take a left turn towards the coffeetable.
Take a butterknife from the top of the tea table.
Turn right and walk straight towards the apple and reach the sink.
Cut the apple into pieces which is kept inside the sink.
Just little bit move towards the left and reach the top of the sink.
Then put the butterknife inside the sink.
Just little bit move towards the right and reach the sink.
Take a piece of apple from the cut apple.
Turn back and take few steps front and again take a left turn to reach the microwave on the table.
Open the oven and put the apple piece inside it and close the oven. After few seconds, open the oven and take the apple out and then close the oven.
Turn left and walk straight and take a right turn to reach the coffeetable.
Put the apple piece on the right top corner of the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple piece on the right top corner of the coffee table.
